1
00:01:31,900 --> 00:01:34,680
=Hot Blooded=

2
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:38,160
=Episode 15=

3
00:02:09,590 --> 00:02:10,530
Jing.

4
00:02:14,950 --> 00:02:16,050
Jing.

5
00:02:21,190 --> 00:02:22,210
Jing!

6
00:02:29,630 --> 00:02:30,470
Rong.

7
00:02:31,540 --> 00:02:32,810
Jing!

8
00:02:36,110 --> 00:02:37,090
Jing!

9
00:02:37,350 --> 00:02:38,190
Uncle.

10
00:02:39,470 --> 00:02:40,400
Uncle.

11
00:02:41,790 --> 00:02:42,630
Jing.

12
00:02:42,630 --> 00:02:43,470
Rong.

13
00:02:45,580 --> 00:02:47,720
- Qigong.
- Rong, stop calling their names.

14
00:02:48,910 --> 00:02:50,440
My uncle's boat

15
00:02:50,740 --> 00:02:51,840
was wrecked by the waves like this.

16
00:02:52,300 --> 00:02:54,650
Guo Jing and my uncle

17
00:02:56,140 --> 00:02:57,580
must have been crushed to pieces.

18
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:58,530
Stop talking nonsense!

19
00:02:59,670 --> 00:03:01,090
Why did I talk nonsense?

20
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:03,020
- Jing!
- Rong.

21
00:03:03,020 --> 00:03:04,050
Qigong.

22
00:03:04,740 --> 00:03:06,770
Rong, you just have to accept reality.

23
00:03:07,820 --> 00:03:08,680
Don't touch me.

24
00:03:19,020 --> 00:03:19,930
Qigong.

25
00:03:20,260 --> 00:03:21,120
Qigong.

26
00:03:23,390 --> 00:03:24,230
Qigong.

27
00:03:25,510 --> 00:03:26,440
Great.

28
00:03:50,190 --> 00:03:51,280
Go look around

29
00:03:51,640 --> 00:03:53,090
and see if there are
any houses on the island.

30
00:03:53,510 --> 00:03:54,560
We can't keep walking like this.

31
00:03:54,790 --> 00:03:56,050
We're in this desolate mountain.

32
00:03:56,470 --> 00:03:57,560
No one will live here.

33
00:03:57,790 --> 00:03:59,090
Just go look around.

34
00:04:02,980 --> 00:04:03,820
What?

35
00:04:04,390 --> 00:04:05,390
You just said you wouldn't

36
00:04:05,390 --> 00:04:06,330
let me suffer grievances.

37
00:04:06,980 --> 00:04:07,910
Now you can't even do

38
00:04:07,910 --> 00:04:08,750
this small thing.

39
00:04:10,140 --> 00:04:11,370
I will go. I will go.

40
00:04:11,580 --> 00:04:12,670
I'll go take a look now.

41
00:04:12,670 --> 00:04:13,530
Rong, wait for me.

42
00:04:15,740 --> 00:04:16,580
Master.

43
00:04:16,580 --> 00:04:17,610
Let's go this way.

44
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:45,050
(The boat suddenly sank.)

45
00:04:47,150 --> 00:04:49,250
(Old Imp disappeared without a trace.)

46
00:04:50,180 --> 00:04:52,490
(Me and Jing drifted for several days)

47
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:55,350
(and saw Ouyang Feng's boat.)

48
00:04:55,350 --> 00:04:56,250
Everything is ready.

49
00:04:56,830 --> 00:04:57,760
Once light the fire,

50
00:04:58,150 --> 00:04:59,970
this big boat will turn into ashes.

51
00:05:00,500 --> 00:05:01,340
Okay.

52
00:05:01,540 --> 00:05:04,640
(They coveted the Nine Yin Manual)

53
00:05:05,230 --> 00:05:06,760
(and wanted to kill us.)

54
00:05:09,060 --> 00:05:09,900
(Later,)

55
00:05:10,540 --> 00:05:12,440
(we fought on the boat.)

56
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:24,560
(I saved Ouyang Feng out of good will.)

57
00:05:24,910 --> 00:05:25,750
(Who would have thought)

58
00:05:26,150 --> 00:05:28,050
(he stabbed me in the back?)

59
00:05:33,180 --> 00:05:34,370
Where is Jing?

60
00:05:42,470 --> 00:05:43,810
Qigong, don't worry.

61
00:05:44,300 --> 00:05:45,730
Jing is a lucky person.

62
00:05:46,110 --> 00:05:47,200
He will be fine.

63
00:05:50,110 --> 00:05:51,370
The most important thing now is

64
00:05:51,670 --> 00:05:53,520
to detoxify the snake venom on you.

65
00:05:56,230 --> 00:05:57,680
I can do that.

66
00:06:04,180 --> 00:06:05,020
Why are you here?

67
00:06:05,620 --> 00:06:06,460
This poison

68
00:06:06,670 --> 00:06:07,830
is the king of all poisons

69
00:06:07,830 --> 00:06:08,760
cultivated by my uncle.

70
00:06:09,940 --> 00:06:10,780
Rong.

71
00:06:11,350 --> 00:06:13,000
We have a telepathic connection.

72
00:06:13,740 --> 00:06:14,930
Since you are not taking me with you,

73
00:06:15,270 --> 00:06:17,000
I can only follow my heart.

74
00:06:17,380 --> 00:06:18,880
Enough with the talk.

75
00:06:19,420 --> 00:06:20,320
Give me the antidote.

76
00:06:22,150 --> 00:06:24,290
I can give it to you,

77
00:06:24,790 --> 00:06:26,760
but not for free.

78
00:06:27,110 --> 00:06:27,970
What do you want?

79
00:06:28,670 --> 00:06:31,930
I want to remove the thorns from you.

80
00:06:32,740 --> 00:06:33,640
Cut to the chase!

81
00:06:35,860 --> 00:06:37,200
You give me the Soft Hedgehog Armor,

82
00:06:37,500 --> 00:06:38,810
and I will give you the antidote.

83
00:06:39,180 --> 00:06:40,020
How is it?

84
00:06:48,380 --> 00:06:50,000
Okay, I'll give it to you.

85
00:06:50,500 --> 00:06:51,370
You go out first.

86
00:06:53,860 --> 00:06:55,880
I'm wearing the Soft Hedgehog Armor.

87
00:06:56,180 --> 00:06:57,110
If you don't go out,

88
00:06:57,110 --> 00:06:58,330
how can I take it off
and give it to you?

89
00:06:58,500 --> 00:07:00,120
Rong, you have always been clever.

90
00:07:00,740 --> 00:07:02,230
If I go out,

91
00:07:02,230 --> 00:07:03,270
and you do something

92
00:07:03,270 --> 00:07:04,250
on the Soft Hedgehog Armor,

93
00:07:04,540 --> 00:07:05,680
what should I do?

94
00:07:06,230 --> 00:07:08,170
There's no one here.

95
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:09,740
Why don't you take off your clothes

96
00:07:09,740 --> 00:07:11,440
one by one

97
00:07:12,060 --> 00:07:14,860
so I can appreciate your beauty?

98
00:07:14,860 --> 00:07:16,410
You deserve a beating, scoundrel!

99
00:07:42,860 --> 00:07:44,610
Little Venomous Creature, unfreeze me.

100
00:07:45,380 --> 00:07:46,220
Rong.

101
00:07:46,590 --> 00:07:47,590
How can I easily

102
00:07:47,590 --> 00:07:49,170
let you go?

103
00:07:49,830 --> 00:07:50,710
Today,

104
00:07:50,710 --> 00:07:52,540
I will get you

105
00:07:52,540 --> 00:07:53,710
and let you see

106
00:07:53,710 --> 00:07:55,490
what makes me better than Guo Jing.

107
00:08:04,710 --> 00:08:05,880
Little beast.

108
00:08:07,180 --> 00:08:08,270
I am here,

109
00:08:08,270 --> 00:08:09,520
and you're still messing around.

110
00:08:10,270 --> 00:08:11,170
You are not poisoned?

111
00:08:14,420 --> 00:08:15,910
Your uncle's dirty tricks

112
00:08:15,910 --> 00:08:17,440
can't work on me.

113
00:08:18,620 --> 00:08:19,560
I disdain to kill you.

114
00:08:20,270 --> 00:08:21,640
But I don't want to see you.

115
00:08:22,420 --> 00:08:23,810
If you come again,

116
00:08:24,350 --> 00:08:26,370
I'll have to take your life.

117
00:08:27,060 --> 00:08:27,900
Get lost.

118
00:08:46,980 --> 00:08:48,040
Great, Master.

119
00:08:48,710 --> 00:08:49,550
You're fine.

120
00:08:52,070 --> 00:08:53,000
Master.

121
00:08:54,780 --> 00:08:56,730
The snake poison is really powerful.

122
00:08:59,500 --> 00:09:01,250
Just by talking,

123
00:09:02,780 --> 00:09:04,250
I couldn't suppress the poison

124
00:09:04,830 --> 00:09:06,250
and let it get into my meridians.

125
00:09:07,140 --> 00:09:08,490
Now I

126
00:09:08,740 --> 00:09:10,730
have lost all my power.

127
00:09:12,070 --> 00:09:13,190
There's no use anymore.

128
00:09:13,190 --> 00:09:14,800
No, it won't happen.

129
00:09:15,140 --> 00:09:15,980
Master.

130
00:09:16,550 --> 00:09:18,040
I'll go find him and get the antidote.

131
00:09:19,110 --> 00:09:20,090
Rong.

132
00:09:21,620 --> 00:09:23,000
You are so smart.

133
00:09:24,070 --> 00:09:27,120
How could you not know
that little beast was deceiving you?

134
00:09:29,140 --> 00:09:29,980
No.

135
00:09:31,900 --> 00:09:33,330
As long as there is a glimmer of hope,

136
00:09:34,350 --> 00:09:35,520
I won't give up.

137
00:09:38,550 --> 00:09:39,760
I can't find Jing.

138
00:09:40,350 --> 00:09:42,250
I can't lose you, either.

139
00:09:47,230 --> 00:09:48,690
Fate is predetermined.

140
00:09:49,620 --> 00:09:51,370
Even if you lose me,

141
00:09:52,550 --> 00:09:54,570
you can't compromise yourself.

142
00:09:56,350 --> 00:09:57,210
No.

143
00:09:58,230 --> 00:09:59,850
I don't have much time left.

144
00:10:01,350 --> 00:10:02,380
If that little beast

145
00:10:02,380 --> 00:10:04,280
found out that I was bluffing,

146
00:10:06,740 --> 00:10:08,970
I can't protect you anymore.

147
00:10:12,230 --> 00:10:13,490
You go by yourself.

148
00:10:14,230 --> 00:10:15,070
No.

149
00:10:15,190 --> 00:10:16,030
Master.

150
00:10:16,230 --> 00:10:17,760
We should leave together.

151
00:10:18,260 --> 00:10:20,090
Jing is missing.

152
00:10:21,110 --> 00:10:23,040
We can't put you in danger too.

153
00:10:27,830 --> 00:10:28,920
Wait until it gets dark.

154
00:10:29,550 --> 00:10:30,390
Master.

155
00:10:30,430 --> 00:10:31,610
I'll take you to find a small boat

156
00:10:31,730 --> 00:10:32,700
and leave here.

157
00:10:50,550 --> 00:10:51,570
What are you here for again?

158
00:10:53,830 --> 00:10:54,670
Sir.

159
00:10:54,860 --> 00:10:56,230
I accidentally

160
00:10:56,230 --> 00:10:57,850
offended Rong.

161
00:10:58,230 --> 00:10:59,640
I feel guilty about it.

162
00:11:00,110 --> 00:11:01,120
Please forgive me.

163
00:11:01,570 --> 00:11:02,430
Don't think that I don't know

164
00:11:02,430 --> 00:11:03,730
what are you up to.

165
00:11:05,740 --> 00:11:08,450
Thinking that
you two have not eaten yet,

166
00:11:08,740 --> 00:11:09,880
I caught a rabbit

167
00:11:10,380 --> 00:11:11,450
and delivered it to you.

168
00:11:12,830 --> 00:11:14,570
If you really mean it,

169
00:11:15,430 --> 00:11:16,690
I appreciate it.

170
00:11:18,110 --> 00:11:19,110
If you came to

171
00:11:19,110 --> 00:11:20,400
check whether I lied,

172
00:11:20,710 --> 00:11:22,040
get started

173
00:11:22,470 --> 00:11:24,000
and don't dawdle.

174
00:11:28,110 --> 00:11:29,000
You must be joking, sir.

175
00:11:29,430 --> 00:11:30,690
I wouldn't dare.

176
00:11:31,350 --> 00:11:32,190
Get lost.

177
00:11:37,310 --> 00:11:38,160
Farewell.

178
00:11:46,470 --> 00:11:47,310
Master.

179
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:50,330
I may fool him once,

180
00:11:50,950 --> 00:11:52,490
but I can't fool him three times.

181
00:11:54,190 --> 00:11:55,030
Rong.

182
00:11:55,660 --> 00:11:58,510
Today I want you
to do something difficult

183
00:11:58,510 --> 00:12:00,370
and against your nature.

184
00:12:01,590 --> 00:12:02,800
Can you do that?

185
00:12:03,860 --> 00:12:05,090
Please tell me.

186
00:12:15,190 --> 00:12:16,030
Kid,

187
00:12:16,950 --> 00:12:17,880
kneel down.

188
00:12:23,950 --> 00:12:26,610
Master, you created the Beggars' Gang,

189
00:12:26,830 --> 00:12:28,160
and passed it down to me.

190
00:12:28,830 --> 00:12:30,330
I failed

191
00:12:30,660 --> 00:12:32,120
to bring glory to our gang.

192
00:12:33,020 --> 00:12:36,370
Today my time is coming,

193
00:12:37,070 --> 00:12:38,760
and I have to take this burden off.

194
00:12:39,620 --> 00:12:41,370
Please bless

195
00:12:42,230 --> 00:12:44,160
this girl in front of me,

196
00:12:44,470 --> 00:12:47,520
and always keep her safe.

197
00:12:47,900 --> 00:12:49,060
Help her bring blessings

198
00:12:49,060 --> 00:12:51,370
to the suffering disciples of our gang.

199
00:12:52,260 --> 00:12:53,100
Master.

200
00:12:53,900 --> 00:12:55,880
Are you going to make me
the Chief of Beggars' Gang?

201
00:12:56,950 --> 00:12:58,090
I can't accept that.

202
00:12:59,830 --> 00:13:01,160
If you refuse,

203
00:13:02,260 --> 00:13:04,970
I will not rest in peace.

204
00:13:08,710 --> 00:13:10,450
Master, I will do that.

205
00:13:10,900 --> 00:13:12,280
Good girl.

206
00:13:19,140 --> 00:13:20,040
The Dog-Beating Staff

207
00:13:20,900 --> 00:13:22,490
is the token of the Chief of our gang.

208
00:13:22,830 --> 00:13:24,040
Now I'm giving it to you.

209
00:13:25,070 --> 00:13:26,250
Come take it.

210
00:13:36,980 --> 00:13:38,160
From now on,

211
00:13:38,430 --> 00:13:40,490
you are the 19th chief
of the Beggars' Gang.

212
00:13:40,780 --> 00:13:42,490
You must escape from here.

213
00:13:43,140 --> 00:13:44,400
On July 15th,

214
00:13:44,900 --> 00:13:46,090
take this Dog-Beating Staff

215
00:13:46,380 --> 00:13:48,450
to the beggars' meeting
by the Dongting Lake.

216
00:13:48,740 --> 00:13:49,690
Beggars' meeting?

217
00:13:50,140 --> 00:13:51,470
The four elders of the gang

218
00:13:51,470 --> 00:13:52,730
and all the leaders

219
00:13:53,190 --> 00:13:54,150
will be waiting for me there

220
00:13:54,150 --> 00:13:55,570
to appoint the next Chief.

221
00:13:57,190 --> 00:13:58,570
When they see this Staff,

222
00:13:59,550 --> 00:14:00,800
they'll know what it means.

223
00:14:01,310 --> 00:14:02,430
But, Master,

224
00:14:02,430 --> 00:14:03,490
I'm still young.

225
00:14:03,780 --> 00:14:05,090
If I become the Chief,

226
00:14:05,620 --> 00:14:07,160
the four elders won't agree.

227
00:14:07,620 --> 00:14:09,330
They dare not.

228
00:14:10,070 --> 00:14:11,490
This has been the rule.

229
00:14:11,980 --> 00:14:14,620
As long as the Chief
of the Beggars' Gang gives an order,

230
00:14:14,620 --> 00:14:17,120
all beggars in the world must obey.

231
00:14:17,860 --> 00:14:19,160
It's a pity

232
00:14:20,590 --> 00:14:22,690
that you, a little girl,

233
00:14:22,950 --> 00:14:25,120
have to deal with all the beggars.

234
00:14:41,470 --> 00:14:42,330
Your Highness.

235
00:14:46,620 --> 00:14:47,460
Father.

236
00:14:47,710 --> 00:14:49,090
Why did you summon me urgently?

237
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:51,550
Do you know why I said the other day

238
00:14:51,550 --> 00:14:53,120
that we must wait for Ouyang Feng?

239
00:14:54,140 --> 00:14:55,000
I don't know.

240
00:14:55,350 --> 00:14:56,880
Ouyang Ke told me

241
00:14:57,230 --> 00:14:58,980
he's going to Peach Blossom Island

242
00:14:58,980 --> 00:15:00,270
with his uncle Ouyang Feng

243
00:15:00,270 --> 00:15:01,690
to find the Nine Yin Manual.

244
00:15:02,190 --> 00:15:03,740
If he fails to obtain the Manual,

245
00:15:03,740 --> 00:15:05,850
he will ask me to send soldiers to help.

246
00:15:06,230 --> 00:15:07,250
As a trade-off,

247
00:15:07,710 --> 00:15:09,350
he will persuade his uncle

248
00:15:09,350 --> 00:15:10,310
to fully help us

249
00:15:10,310 --> 00:15:11,850
get the Book of Wumu.

250
00:15:12,740 --> 00:15:13,580
Now,

251
00:15:13,900 --> 00:15:15,070
I've already received

252
00:15:15,070 --> 00:15:16,280
a letter from Mr. Ouyang,

253
00:15:16,660 --> 00:15:17,920
asking me to send troops.

254
00:15:18,380 --> 00:15:19,280
That's great.

255
00:15:20,500 --> 00:15:22,490
If Ouyang Feng can help us,

256
00:15:23,260 --> 00:15:25,280
we will easily obtain the Book of Wumu.

257
00:15:26,460 --> 00:15:27,780
I'm willing to go
to Peach Blossom Island

258
00:15:27,780 --> 00:15:28,850
together with you

259
00:15:29,900 --> 00:15:31,760
to assist Mr. Ouyang.

260
00:15:36,260 --> 00:15:38,330
I must teach you
the Dog Beating Staff Technique

261
00:15:38,980 --> 00:15:40,850
while I can still move.

262
00:15:41,260 --> 00:15:42,400
Dog Beating Staff Technique?

263
00:15:43,310 --> 00:15:44,230
What kind of dog

264
00:15:44,230 --> 00:15:45,150
needs to get beatened

265
00:15:45,150 --> 00:15:46,020
with a kind of technique?

266
00:15:46,020 --> 00:15:49,570
Since ancient times,
poor people would be bullied by dogs.

267
00:15:49,900 --> 00:15:51,260
You have never been poor,

268
00:15:51,260 --> 00:15:52,100
so you don't know

269
00:15:52,710 --> 00:15:53,860
those vicious dogs

270
00:15:53,860 --> 00:15:55,690
specifically target poor
and vulnerable families.

271
00:15:55,950 --> 00:15:57,730
If there are too many
vicious dogs on the road,

272
00:15:58,310 --> 00:15:59,250
and they can't be driven away,

273
00:15:59,830 --> 00:16:01,450
can't we use a weapon to beat them?

274
00:16:02,190 --> 00:16:03,030
I got it.

275
00:16:03,430 --> 00:16:04,610
Bad people are like vicious dogs,

276
00:16:05,190 --> 00:16:06,800
and that lecher
is just a despicable dog.

277
00:16:10,550 --> 00:16:12,490
The 36 styles of
Dog Beating Staff Techniques

278
00:16:13,310 --> 00:16:15,370
were created by our grandmaster.

279
00:16:16,740 --> 00:16:19,110
It's always been passed down

280
00:16:19,110 --> 00:16:20,450
to the next Chief by the last one.

281
00:16:21,350 --> 00:16:22,920
Never passing it on to an outsider.

282
00:16:24,140 --> 00:16:25,760
Study it carefully.

283
00:16:34,430 --> 00:16:36,040
The first style.

284
00:17:01,950 --> 00:17:02,790
Master.

285
00:17:05,660 --> 00:17:06,570
It's okay.

286
00:17:10,940 --> 00:17:11,890
Keep practicing.

287
00:17:33,830 --> 00:17:35,360
The second style.

288
00:17:41,750 --> 00:17:43,800
The third style.

289
00:17:49,620 --> 00:17:51,450
The fourth style.

290
00:18:05,860 --> 00:18:07,320
Master, how is it?

