597
00:33:24,220 --> 00:33:25,060
Master.

598
00:33:25,380 --> 00:33:26,220
Master.

599
00:33:36,030 --> 00:33:36,870
Up.

600
00:33:46,140 --> 00:33:47,600
Stop, stop.

601
00:33:48,790 --> 00:33:49,630
Ke.

602
00:33:50,660 --> 00:33:52,450
Uncle, Uncle.

603
00:33:55,550 --> 00:33:56,390
Let's lift again.

604
00:33:57,350 --> 00:33:58,190
No.

605
00:33:58,460 --> 00:33:59,750
This stone is too big.

606
00:33:59,750 --> 00:34:01,210
If Qigong wasn't poisoned,

607
00:34:01,510 --> 00:34:02,660
the four of us will definitely

608
00:34:02,660 --> 00:34:03,650
be able to move this stone.

609
