615
00:34:23,150 --> 00:34:23,990
on Peach Blossom Island.

616
00:34:24,300 --> 00:34:25,210
Winch?

617
00:34:27,910 --> 00:34:28,750
Jing.

618
00:34:29,030 --> 00:34:30,030
We go cut some bamboo

619
00:34:30,030 --> 00:34:31,070
before the tide comes in

620
00:34:31,070 --> 00:34:31,910
to make a winch.

621
00:34:32,470 --> 00:34:33,310
Okay.

622
00:34:38,430 --> 00:34:39,270
Uncle.

623
00:34:39,740 --> 00:34:40,580
Uncle.

624
00:34:40,870 --> 00:34:41,710
Uncle.

625
00:34:42,030 --> 00:34:43,610
It hurts, Uncle.

626
00:34:44,180 --> 00:34:45,740
Just kill me with one strike.

627
00:34:45,740 --> 00:34:46,580
Bear with it.

628
00:34:47,620 --> 00:34:48,460
Bear with it.

629
00:35:47,590 --> 00:35:48,430
Rong.

630
00:35:52,510 --> 00:35:53,650
Thank you.

631
00:35:54,550 --> 00:35:55,480
You don't need to thank me.

632
00:35:56,470 --> 00:35:58,390
Don't you know I set up this mechanism?

633
00:35:58,390 --> 00:35:59,230
Keep it down.

634
00:36:00,470 --> 00:36:01,880
Don't let my uncle hear you.

635
00:36:02,430 --> 00:36:03,530
He will kill you.

636
00:36:09,390 --> 00:36:10,840
Actually, I knew it long ago.

637
00:36:12,620 --> 00:36:13,760
But I'm willing

638
00:36:15,740 --> 00:36:17,170
to die

639
00:36:18,390 --> 00:36:19,530
in your hand.

640
00:36:22,700 --> 00:36:23,610
Why isn't it ready yet?

641
00:36:23,910 --> 00:36:24,950
The tide has already risen.

642
00:36:24,950 --> 00:36:25,880
Why rush me?

643
00:36:26,180 --> 00:36:27,020
It's done.

644
00:37:16,990 --> 00:37:17,830
Uncle.

645
00:37:22,660 --> 00:37:23,500
Uncle.

646
00:37:23,700 --> 00:37:24,540
It's just

647
00:37:25,470 --> 00:37:26,920
a little bit short.

648
00:37:28,390 --> 00:37:29,480
You all leave.

649
00:37:31,550 --> 00:37:33,170
Let me be alone with Ke for a while.

650
00:37:34,300 --> 00:37:35,140
Should we...

651
00:37:48,300 --> 00:37:49,690
We have tried our best.

652
00:37:50,300 --> 00:37:51,140
Yes.

653
00:37:51,700 --> 00:37:53,530
I'm just worried once Ouyang Ke dies,

654
00:37:56,030 --> 00:37:57,110
Ouyang Feng will definitely come

655
00:37:57,110 --> 00:37:58,050
to us for trouble.

656
00:37:58,590 --> 00:38:00,210
Master is seriously injured now.

657
00:38:01,180 --> 00:38:02,570
The two of us are no match for him.

658
00:38:05,700 --> 00:38:06,780
Ouyang Ke

659
00:38:06,780 --> 00:38:07,690
had it coming.

660
00:38:08,140 --> 00:38:09,660
If he didn't harm me and Qigong,

661
00:38:09,660 --> 00:38:10,960
he wouldn't have ended up like this.

662
00:38:11,990 --> 00:38:13,550
If Ouyang Feng wants to come,
let him come.

663
00:38:13,550 --> 00:38:14,470
I'm not afraid of him.

664
00:38:14,470 --> 00:38:15,780
Master is still seriously injured.

665
00:38:15,780 --> 00:38:16,620
Rong.

666
00:38:18,510 --> 00:38:19,360
You are the smartest.

667
00:38:19,700 --> 00:38:21,030
Why don't you think about

668
00:38:21,030 --> 00:38:21,880
some other way?

669
00:38:23,950 --> 00:38:25,010
If the tide doesn't rise,

670
00:38:25,430 --> 00:38:26,800
