until the tide recedes, right?

675
00:38:35,390 --> 00:38:36,230
That's right.

676
00:38:41,430 --> 00:38:42,270
Hold breath?

677
00:38:48,870 --> 00:38:49,710
Jing.

678
00:38:50,470 --> 00:38:51,320
I have a way now.

679
00:38:51,820 --> 00:38:53,430
- Uncle.
- Ke. Ke.

680
00:38:53,430 --> 00:38:54,840
Uncle, I'm scared.

681
00:38:55,550 --> 00:38:56,400
Ke, don't be afraid.

682
00:38:58,660 --> 00:38:59,920
I'm here with you.

683
00:39:02,260 --> 00:39:03,360
I'm afraid

684
00:39:05,390 --> 00:39:06,590
I can't

685
00:39:06,590 --> 00:39:08,250
escape this.

686
00:39:09,950 --> 00:39:11,010
No, Ke.

687
00:39:13,140 --> 00:39:14,440
Uncle is here.

688
00:39:16,260 --> 00:39:19,400
I have something

689
00:39:21,140 --> 00:39:22,480
to ask you.

690
00:39:25,430 --> 00:39:26,400
Tell me, Ke.

691
00:39:29,390 --> 00:39:30,650
When I was young,

692
00:39:32,820 --> 00:39:36,320
I heard that on the Mount White Camel,

693
00:39:37,510 --> 00:39:38,690
there was a woman

694
00:39:40,260 --> 00:39:41,880
who often looked southward,

695
00:39:43,140 --> 00:39:47,130
waiting for her lover.

696
00:39:49,950 --> 00:39:51,570
But after waiting for many years,

697
00:39:53,550 --> 00:39:55,400
her beloved never returned.

698
00:39:57,780 --> 00:39:59,010
Later,

699
00:40:00,550 --> 00:40:01,920
she married

700
00:40:04,260 --> 00:40:06,610
her lover's brother,

701
00:40:09,620 --> 00:40:11,090
and became his sister-in-law.

702
00:40:14,820 --> 00:40:16,610
On the night of her wedding,

703
00:40:17,620 --> 00:40:19,480
her lover suddenly came back.

704
00:40:22,140 --> 00:40:25,090
But everything was already set in stone.

705
00:40:27,110 --> 00:40:29,690
Although they missed each other,

706
00:40:31,470 --> 00:40:33,440
they still violated moral ethics,

707
00:40:34,140 --> 00:40:35,400
and gave birth to a child.

708
00:40:39,180 --> 00:40:41,050
To cover this up,

709
00:40:42,990 --> 00:40:44,530
she wanted her son

710
00:40:46,030 --> 00:40:47,610
to call her lover

711
00:40:48,780 --> 00:40:50,400
Uncle instead.

712
00:40:52,700 --> 00:40:53,540
Uncle.

713
00:40:55,700 --> 00:40:58,050
Uncle, is this true?

714
00:41:09,820 --> 00:41:10,660
Uncle.

715
00:41:13,110 --> 00:41:14,130
During my whole life,

716
00:41:15,430 --> 00:41:17,760
