717
00:41:22,820 --> 00:41:23,660
Should I

718
00:41:25,140 --> 00:41:26,840
call you Uncle

719
00:41:29,070 --> 00:41:30,530
or

720
00:41:32,180 --> 00:41:33,020
Father?

721
00:41:53,910 --> 00:41:54,750
There is a way!

722
00:42:00,300 --> 00:42:01,180
You let him

723
00:42:01,180 --> 00:42:02,360
