727
00:42:12,510 --> 00:42:13,530
Listen to me.

728
00:42:22,620 --> 00:42:23,460
Okay.

729
00:42:26,340 --> 00:42:27,280
Uncle.

730
00:42:31,140 --> 00:42:31,980
Okay.

